snippet.title: SkullDash - Doom II Mod Trailer
snippet.description:
Hello all!

SkullDash development is now back in full-swing!
To keep your saliva ducts active I present you a short trailer. I'm going to apologize about the shoddy-ness of the SkullDash Logo, for some reason youtube pixelated the hell out of it. Looks as crisp as the original image before the upload.

Development is now resumed so expect more new map playthroughs in the near future!

I am looking for ACS / DECORATE coders to help out about the place, and if anyone's interested, someone capable of coding a few boss monsters with their own maps.
IF you're interested, get in touch via the comments below!
